<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Fees</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.16.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h2>Scholarship fees</h2>
        <p><strong>Note:</strong> The <strong>Driving license</strong> categories and classes in Romania, vehicle permitted to drive, requirements and driving school tuition fees.</p>
        <div id="accordion">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <a class="card-link" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseOne">
                        Category A
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse show" data-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <pre>
        AM (Moped)

        Age:  16 years minimum
        Passengers: No
        Type:  Motorcycle
        Driving Course Cost: Ksh. 7,500 (average)
        A1 (Light Motorcycle)
            
            
             
        Age: 18 years minimum
        Passengers: Yes (maximum load 60 Kg)
        Type: Motorcycle
        Driving Course Cost: Ksh. 7,500 (Average)
        A2 (Motorcycle taxi, Couriers and 3-wheelers)
            
        Age: 18 years minimum
        Passengers: Yes (maximum load 100 Kg)
        Type: Motorcycle
        Driving Course Cost: Ksh. 7,500 (Average)
        A3 (Motorcycle Three Wheelers)
            
        Age: 18 years minimum
        Passengers: Maximum 3
        Type: Motorcycle
        Driving Course Cost: Ksh. 7,500(Average)
        </pre>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <a class="collapsed card-link" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseTwo">
                        Category B
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <pre>
        B1 (Light Vehicle Automatic)

        Age: 18 years minimum
        Passengers: Maximum 7
        Type: Car
        Driving Course Cost: Ksh. 13,500 (Average)
        B2 (Light Vehicle)
            
        Age: 18 years minimum
        Passengers: No
        Type: Car
        Driving Course Cost: Ksh. 13,500 (Average)
        B3 (Professional)
            
        Age: 21 minimum
        Passengers: Maximum 7
        Type: Car
        Driving Course Cost: Ksh. 10,000 (Average)
            
          </pre>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <a class="collapsed card-link" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseThree">
                        Category C
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <pre>
        C1 (Light Truck)

        Age: 22 – 65 years (with B2 license for at least 2 years)
        Passengers: No
        Type: Truck
        Driving Course Cost: Ksh. 14,500 (Average)
        C (Medium Truck)

        Age: 24 -65 years (with 2 years experience of driving category C1)
        Passengers: No
        Type: Truck
        Driving Course Cost: Ksh. 14,500(Average)
        CE (Heavy Truck with Trailer)

        Age: 28 – 65 years (with 4 years experience of driving category C)
        Passengers: No
        Type: Heavy Truck (articulated)
        Driving Course Cost: Ksh. 27,000 (Average)
        CD (Heavy Good Vehicle for Transportation of Hazardous Materials)

        Age: 30 – 65 years (with 2 years experience of driving category CE)
        Passengers: No
        Type: Heavy Truck (articulated)
        Driving Course Cost: Ksh. 27,000 (Average)

        </pre>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <a class="collapsed card-link" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseFour">
                        Category D
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseFour" class="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <pre>
          D1 (Van)

          Age: 22 – 65 years
          Passengers: Maximum 14
          Type: Van
          Driving Course Cost: Ksh. 10,000 (Average)
          D2 (Minibus)
          
          Age: 25 – 65 years (with 3 years experience of driving category D1)
          Passengers: 14 to 32
          Type: Bus
          Driving Course Cost: Ksh. 10,000(Average)
          D3 (Large Bus)
          
          Age: 30 – 65 years (with 3 years experience of driving category D2)
          Passengers: 33 or more
          Type: Bus
          Driving Course Cost: Ksh. 10,000(Average)
          D4
          
          Age: Maximum 65 years (with 3 years experience of Driving category D3)
          Passengers: Yes
          Type: Articulated Bus
          Driving Course Cost: Ksh. 10,000(Average)

        </pre>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <a class="collapsed card-link" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseFive">
                        Category E
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseFive" class="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <pre>
            Age: 21 – 65 years (Licensed as EC1, EC, ECE, ED, ED1, ED2 and ECD3)
            Passengers: yes
            Type: Special Professional
          </pre>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <a class="collapsed card-link" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseSix">
                        Category F (Persons with Disability)
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseSix" class="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <pre>
          Age: 18 years minimum (must have valid medical certificate, assessment report or disability certificate)
          Type: Can drive any vehicle that one is qualified.
        </pre>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <a class="collapsed card-link" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseSeven">
                        Category G
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseSeven" class="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <pre>
      Passengers: No

      Type: Industrial, Construction and Agricultural (Plants and Equipment operator)
      Driving Course Cost: Ksh. 45,000 (Average)

        </pre>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>